主要翻译
 
horde n (crowd: of people)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 一大群 yí dà qún  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 一伙人 yí dà qún，yì huǒ rén 
 -- A horde of fans greeted the rock stars when they arrived at the airport.
 
horde n (group, swarm: of animals)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 一群（动物） yì qún dòng wù  
 -- A horde of bees suddenly swarmed around the tree.
 
horde n historical (Mongol tribe)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese （游牧的）蒙古部落 yóu mù de měng gǔ bù luò  (历史用语)
 -- The horde lived on the same land for many generations.

其他翻译
 
horde ▦ vi (gather in a crowd)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 集群 jí qún  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 成群结队 jí qún，chéng qún jié duì 
 -- Fans horded around the celebrity.

